    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>Standard Racial Traits</h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Ability Score Modifiers</span>: Paragon (+4&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\">Str</a>, –2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Int</a>, –2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Wisdom-Wis-\">Wis</a>, –2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Cha</a>)&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Advanced&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\">Strength</a>&nbsp;(+2)&nbsp;</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Type</span>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Monstrous-Humanoid\">Monstrous humanoid</a>&nbsp;</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Size</span>: Large (+2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\">Str</a>, -2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\">Dex</a>)</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Base Speed</span>: Normal&nbsp;</li>\n<li><strong>Burrow:</strong>&nbsp;Trox have the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Burrow-Ex-\">burrow</a>&nbsp;movement ability. They gain a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/monsters-foes/#Burrow\">burrow</a>&nbsp;speed of 20 feet.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Languages</span>: Xenophobic&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Senses</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Darkvision:</strong> Trox have&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Darkvision\">darkvision</a>&nbsp;and so can see perfectly in the dark up to 60 feet.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Offensive Racial Abilities</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Frenzy:</strong> Once per day, whenever a trox takes damage, it flies into a frenzy for 1 minute, gaining a +2 racial bonus to Constitution and Strength, but a –2 penalty to AC.</li>\n<li><strong>Grabbing appendages:</strong>&nbsp;Trox have a small group of appendages that are useful for little more than to aid in grappling. They gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/improved-grapple-combat\">Improved Grapple</a>&nbsp;as a bonus feat, and can maintain a grapple and still make attacks with their main appendages.</li>\n</ul>",
